testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.SiteServiceSpec

testcase.name: The site extent can be converted to geojson
A new site can be created
A new site should not allow the siteId to be supplied
Any POIs supplied with a new site should be assigned IDs
New sites without a centroid should have one assigned
